This means you can use a color theme to quickly customize the look of your site
without needing to write any CSS. You can select the color theme in your &lt;code>config.toml&lt;/code> file. Scroll down to find:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Style your site typography</title><link>https://mhicks.me/blog/fonts/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mhicks.me/blog/fonts/</guid><description>&lt;p>As with 
